column6: Qianse Golden Life Rolling Ball Brown Austrian Crystal Pendant Necklace with Rose Gold Long Chain
column14:
With square facets on this translucent brown topaz/chocolate colored pendant, it really catches the light and sparkles as you move. With the pendant in two pieces, you could actually choose to remove the top piece with the embedded crystals and just wear the "stone" section although they work really well together so not sure why you would!

The diameter of the pendant is approximately 1 3/4" so quite big. The chain on this necklace is VERY long (approx. 32"), coming way below my bust line along with being quite thick. Obviously folks with larger chests will find that this necklace sits further up. There are 3 rings of crystals on the top pendant.

The necklace is presented in a quality gift box and once opened you will find it in a sealed plastic bag inside. In a separate box in the sealed outer package is a very pretty blue silk-like scarf (approximately 18" x 19").

PLEASE remember this is fashion jewelry. It is only rose gold plated. Due to its design, this necklace is definitely not going to suit everyone but if you like big, long, sparkly and brown tones then chances are you will love this.

Product was provided in exchange for an honest review. Thanks, Liz

Sterling Silver Oxidized Cubic Zirconia Celtic Knot Hinged Bangle Bracelet, 7.25\" Jewelry 5 0 0 Y N Beautiful Bracelet at a Very Fair Price I got this pretty Celtic Knot bracelet for my girlfriend as one of her anniversary gifts and she loved it! I find it very difficult (like many men) to pick out jewelry for my girl. Most women are very particular about their style, so I was pleased she liked it so much.

It came in a simple black cardboard and velvet presentation box which contrasted the beautiful sterling silver of the piece very nicely. The bracelet we received looks exactly like the photos shown on the Amazon page. Please look closely at the photos as this piece is intentionally \\\"distressed\\\\\". By distressed I mean that it has areas with light tarnish and surface pitting at the intersections of the Celtic knot, and the rest of the bracelet finish almost looks lightly brushed in places, with a more polished finish in others. My girlfriend says this is meant to be a more of a casual-wear accent piece and the slightly distressed finish is part of its beauty and charm.

The cubic zirconia diamonds are quite small but I did notice them sparkling nicely in bright light. The bracelet is incredibly easy to put on and take off by simply squeezing the band slightly and removing the hook from the loop. Looking at the quality and casual charm of the piece, I thought it was a very good value, and considering her reaction, I think my girlfriend believes it was a lot more expensive than it was.

***** HIGHLY RECOMMENDED! - 5 STAR *****"

column6: 18k Yellow Gold-Plated Sterling Silver Two-Tone Double-Hoop Earrings
column14:
t I really love the two-tone color of these. They match both my gold and my silver color jewelry, and especially items that have both colors (like coins with bezels or something.) They are sterling with gold plating, so I am careful with putting mine away to protect the yellow gold part from scratching. They are mirror image of each other which is great so that they match directionally (like silver on the outside of each side of your head...or vice versa depending on how you put them on.) Sometimes earrings don't do that and it bugs me.

Diameter of the hoop part is just slightly smaller than a nickel (not counting the post part which sticks up slightly.) So, if you want to gauge the size, hold a nickel up to your ear! I have purchased many items of jewelry from the amazon collection and am rarely disappointed. The items are described well and the photos are accurate.

column6: Sterling Silver Blood Red Teardrop Earrings
column14: I am always looking for a beautiful pair of earrings and this set did not disappoint.  They are much prettier in person than they are in this picture.  The color is much more vibrant than I expected and that is a good thing.  I love the little faint lines in the teardrops themselves.  They give an added detail that is not really noticeable unless you look closely.  I prefer to wear Sterling silver earrings or gold because fake earrings tend to hurt my ears.  Since these are Sterling Silver I had no issues with ear pain.  These earrings are not heavy on my lobes and they are very comfortable to wear.  These earrings stayed in my lobes and I had no issues with them falling out.  They come in a little bag and placed in a nice little box.  I am very happy with these earrings.  I have received a few compliments already.  All opinions stated are that of my own and have in no way been swayed. At least it looks sort of pretty, and the gem might be good for something. The chain however is too small to even fit around a toddler's neck, though it is very pretty, it's useless. Even for as cheap as I bought it for, I thought it would at least be somewhat useful, but I was definitely wrong. Maybe it can be used as a Christmas ornament, but then again it's so tiny it would just get lost in the branches. Now I know it's cheap, but why even sell something like this? Is it really that much more expensive to make it slightly bigger, stay in place durable, and give us a chain that will actually fit somebody? Honestly. Disappointed.

column14:
This a fantastic and wonderfully pretty,delicate jewelry set! Although delicate appearing, it has substantial weight and doesn't feel cheap.

I paid less than two dollars for this set and was completely surprised at its beauty and appearance! The colors are a bit lighter than the pictures, but this is a plus. It looks like this is enameled and much more expensive than it is. It gives a delicate, pastel appearance and I wore it with a very pale pink sweater and got tons of compliments!

I don't wear the pieces together which would look to "matchy-matchy", but separately, they can go with many outfits and other pieces of jewelry. Thin necklaces could be layered with this necklace and look lovely. And I could see the earrings worn with strings of pearls! This was a truly great buy and I highly recommend it!!
